Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In the province of Trois, there is\Na town of lakes and glass: Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kanata Sorami and\NI aspire to become a trumpeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to the fortress of the 1121st Platoon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2773,2920,\4a&HFF\3a&HFF)}and have met many people there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the gunner: Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's younger than me, but she enlisted before me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(4096,4196,\3a&HFF\4a&HFF)\t(4120,4196,\1a&HFF)}so she's both my senior and like a little sister, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(110,0)\pos(240,262)}She was acting a bit cold {(tsun-tsun)}at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2400,2400,\4a&H60\3a&H60)\t(2407,2530,\4a&HFF\3a&HFF)}but we're great friends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is the pilot and mechanic, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She was pretty taciturn\Nso at first I thought she didn't like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but she just doesn't talk much\Nand is actually a very kind girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's also very smart, always reading difficult books
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.76,0:00:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2780,2780,\4a&H80\3a&H80)\t(2781,2900,\4a&HFF\3a&HFF)}and does maintenance on the Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, I forgot about the commander!{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Filicia Heideman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like a mother or big sister to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:01:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(5110,5110,\4a&H70\3a&H70)\t(5121,5247,\4a&HFF\3a&HFF)}Her cooking is great and we all really look up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person I admire {'respect' is more literal but eh}the most:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rio, also a trumpeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She had to leave the Time-Telling Fortress\Nfor a while due to family matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but she was able to come back for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,0)}Rio returning was like finding a missing note.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The story of the 1121st Platoon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3186,3186,\4a&H80\3a&H80)\t(3187,3320,\4a&HFF\3a&HFF)}can play out once again.{The verb used means, like, it can be played as a musical performance, can't put it in english well}{Vin: it's a tricky line indeed.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful things, sullied things...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,hardships but fun times, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3360,3360,\4a&H50\3a&H50)\t(3363,3500,\4a&HFF\3a&HFF)}Happiness, and also pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the maidens of the fortress
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx83}are performing as a quintet again, in a far-off corner of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, as the curtain is raised...
